            <title>[FLINK-30214] The resource is not enough</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-30214</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When turn up the parallelism, the resources isn&apos;t enough for MiniCluster. I&apos;m not sure whether the flink on yarn or k8s is right? I can test later.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I guess the parallelism should be changed in a right place. And we should add more unit test or ITCase to check these cases. And it&apos;s my honor to make these improvements and bug fixes.&lt;/p&gt;

